title: Born Free
transcripts:
Born Free - a world of wonderful award winning products for babies and toddlers. Born Free bottles, pacifiers and training cups are made of the highest quality materials and have always been 100% BPA free.

The exclusive Born Free venting system reduces air pressure in the bottle so liquids flow smoothly and it's easier for baby to suckle. This makes for a smooth transition from breast to bottle and also reduces colic and middle ear infections.

Born Free products are easy to clean and assemble. Choose between theh glass bottle with the silicone sleeve and the 100% safe plastic bottle that can withstand the freezer, microwave, heating and dishwasher. It's even shatter proof.

Born Free bottles are well designed and don't leak. Your baby stays dry and so does the crib, stroller and diaper bag.

Born Free's orthodontically correct pacifiers, teething aides and nipples help baby's teeth develop properly.

Born Free's safe and smart system grows with your child. Interchangeable parts make for a smooth transition from bottle to cup. It's easy for baby and economical for you.

I recommend that parents choose a teething system for their baby that's designed both for comfort and for health. Born Free is a world leader in this technology.

Insist on the world's leading BPA free brand.

Born Free - smart, safe and simply the best.
